These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk, mirinda, juice
City: colone, miami, prague, london, venice, rome
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person traveling to venice is between the person drinking juice and the person traveling to colone##2
5. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to miami##2
6. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Beverage           | sprite | soy-milk | juice | mirinda | almond-milk    | cola  |
| City   | rome | miami   | london       | venice        | colone | prague |

