.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, pop, ambient, blues, metal, folk
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, june, may, november, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan metal##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the fan blues and the fan techno##2
4. the fan ambient is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the fan techno is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the fan blues is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the fan pop is on the left of the fan folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | pop | folk | metal | blues | ambient | techno  |
| Birthday           | march | december  | july | june    | november  | may |

