.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
House: modern, cottage, futuristic, palace, gothic-revival, farmhouse
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: disco, jazz, ambient, electronic, soul, d&b
1. the modern house is on the left of the fan disco##1
2. the palace house is the fan soul##1
3. the fan disco is on the left of the fan electronic##1
4. the fan disco is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
6. the gothic-revival house is between the palace house and the fan disco##2
7. the fan jazz is on the far left##1
8. the fan ambient is on the right of the palace house##1
9. the cottage house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| House         | cottage | modern | farmhouse      | gothic-revival | palace | futuristic      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b  | disco | electronic   | soul       | ambient |

