.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, horse, snake
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, balloon-flower, orchid, marigold, sunflower
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is the owner of the snake##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who growssunflower##2
9. the owner of the goat is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Pet    | goat | snake | horse  | hedgehog      | guinea-pig | ferret  |
| Flower   | begonia  | balloon-flower    | orchid | daffodil | marigold | sunflower |

