1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
4. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in february##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Cigar       | davidoff | bluemaster | dannemann | siglo | aristoff | bolivar |
| Birthday   | march | december    | february  | april    | august    | july    |

