3. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
4. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking water##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing billiard and the person playing poker##2
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
