.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, orange, brown, blood-red, lavender
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, november, december, august, march, april
 1. the person who likes lavender is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who likes mauve and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Color   | mauve   | blood-red  | turquise | brown | lavender | orange     |
| Birthday   | november | july | april    | march | august | december |

