.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory, coral, lilac, grey, brown
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, martial-arts, mystery, horror, thriller, sports
 1. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 2. the person who likes grey is the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who likes coral##2
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is between the person watching action movies and the person who likes ivory##2
10. the person who likes lilac is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Color         | brown   | grey | coral       | lilac | yellow    | ivory |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | thriller  | mystery | action      | horror | sports        |

