The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, august, june, december, january, may
 1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who likes coral is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes pink and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes mauve##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Color           | coral      | pink | ivory | mauve   | ebony  | aquamarine |
| Birthday   | december | september  | august             | may | june | january       |

