.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
City: rome, paris, liverpool, london, marseilles, prague
The people have 6 different hobbies: reading, gardening, skydiving, photography, board-games, chess
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person traveling to paris##2
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 6. the person traveling to london is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| City   | london     | rome | marseilles   | liverpool     | prague       | paris       |
| Hobby    | gardening | photography   | reading | board-games | chess | skydiving |

