 5. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the owner of the horse##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

