 4. the person playing bridge is the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person playing whist is the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching family movies and the person watching musical movies##2
10. the person watching scientific movies is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts | musical | spy | family | scientific | romance |
| Game   | go | domino | mah-jongg      | bridge     | canasta       | whist |

 